    <h1>5 Lessons Sebastião Salgado Has Taught Me About Street Photography</h1>
    <div class="primo-paragrafo">
        <p>I recently saw Sebastião Salgado’s “Genesis” exhibition in Toronto about a year ago,
             and was blown away by the body of work. It was the most ambitious project I had ever seen– essentially Salgado aimed to
             photograph the entire world. He photographed people, landscapes, and nature– and did so over 8 years and all around the globe.</p>
